</p>
<p>

The value of this equilibrium 
<answer inline='true'>
<choiceinput>
<choice credit='1'>does</choice>
<choice>does not</choice>
</choiceinput>
</answer>
 depend on the value of the parameter <m>c</m>.
 </p>

<p>Under what conditions are there more than one equilibrium? <m>b =</m> 
<answer>
